    <briefdescription>
<para>Provides the generic part of the linear regression methods. </para>    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class provides implements the generic part of the linear regression method. It is independent of the specific choice of basis functions. These basis functions are defined via the <ref refid="classkukadu_1_1TrajectoryGenerator" kindref="compound">TrajectoryGenerator</ref> class. </para>    </detaileddescription>
